Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,True Calendar year 71.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity, 70% of whom had been sent out into space, was largely divided into two powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dorssia Military Pact Federation, which developed out of military alliances,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and ARUS, the transatlantic treaty organization which expanded trade alliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying between these two superpowers, there was a third state that had gained economic prosperity:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A proponent of peace through neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they had been enjoying the blessings of peace and tranquility,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the course of history took a sharp turn towards chaos as a result of a sneak attack by the Dorssian military.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is that he isn't a Sakimori Academy student,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but is actually a Dorssian soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything else about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His name. It's "L-elf".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I give my word that your interrogation will be conducted in accordance with the New Guinea Treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A hand mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake. A riot 3:14 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer lies behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the ARUS Lunar Orbital Forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the ARUS Lunar Orbital Forces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Line up and wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.61,Alt,,0,0,0,,Are there any injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:47.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Senator Figaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The only adults left here are myself and Mr. Kibukawa, the physics teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, it's the least we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We of ARUS and JIOR are friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like forever since last time I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even though we had classes just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At the shrine, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.69,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an2}At the shrine, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so cool, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,The herd's triumphant return, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not a—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, here's my address!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haruto. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I can't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been saved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,During the New Guinea Conflict two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you kept our brigade of 5,000 men pinned down all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, we've called you the One-man Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined that you would be so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the worlds GDP leader for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's policeman! The land of freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always count on ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the sensation of being held tight by polymerized carbon cermet armor... What a rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost myself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm out of those tattered rags, I feel like a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd tell him how you felt if we survived, who did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to regret something said than unsaid. If you're just not sure, just come out and tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, our life coach says so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like Nanami has a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Haruto doesn't really know, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he found the robot, and when he got in, he knew how to fight in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe that Haruto of all people would have a knack for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... happened at all. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Temperature and pulse, both normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can't call that normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have a doctor look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The military should have doctors with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that if i were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd just use him as a lab rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults are sleazeballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukino, did something happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruto! Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You attacked him, right out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you were a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that other time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, I'm not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what I'll to do you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You used that power to save us all, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Tokishima in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator Figaro says he'd like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator Figaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... It's good to meet you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...Figaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Senator...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never talked to a politician before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think that I'm not as scary as those Dorssian forces you defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was through these posts that we learned you were still putting up a fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The user who uploaded the video was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rainbow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If wonder if it's one of our students?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not post something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People around the world are worried about your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you post, the people of JIOR might see it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine. We were saved by the ARUS military.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look! That high school boy says he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be around the same age as us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.12,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wonderful news has just come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.57,Alt,,0,0,0,,We're told that that high school boy has posted a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! Let us invite you to our match!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way! Was that the Goal King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was. Best-selling authors, gold medalists, and even our president have friended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This says your friend count is over 700 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The high schooler who took on the mighty Dorssian military all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They've given you the tagline,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Boy Who Took on the World.''
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now the last hope of JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The symbol of the fight against Dorssia's schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you telling me that I have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No. To run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What we drove off was just a single frontline unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If the main force that occupied your Sphere comes at you, you won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a soldier. I'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, running isn't losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really losing is when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, surviving is a sort of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help us, Haruto Tokishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To help everyone survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a nutrient solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Failing to feed a prisoner is a treaty violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights! Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will now commence Plan D7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your retrieving us was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to participate in the recapture of Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You appear to be a man short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For L-elf of all people to have—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is that he inflicted casualties on our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not averse to the word "friendship", you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Valvrave has the absolute highest priority of all special missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will overlook any irregularities resulting from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Recover the Valvrave without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Form up by classes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure that the students before and after your student number are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right! Just follow the military's instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, can we really get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll protect you in the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all counting on you, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he cooperating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The choice that avoids fighting is the best choice. That's so Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really get him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They grew up together. Shoko and Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Join the evacuation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're at cable car #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Student Council President Renkoboji went to make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone call? At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a lot on his plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Anyway, join the evacuation right away, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the command form?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's snooty to the core, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's coming! How long are you going to stay cooped up in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you're gonna end up left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bugging me, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,This is war! If you stay—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—? Hey! Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush! You can all fit in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS will help us, so please don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hand mic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A hand mic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the difference in relative troop strengths, their only choice is to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If they intend to conduct a smooth retreat, using a student is the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Influence, ideology, docility...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The conclusion this leads me to is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dorssian prisoner has escaped!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Height, 177cm! Hair, silver! Male! Age, 17!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Capture upon discovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, the Dorssian prisoner has...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it took them 15 minutes to discover I had escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Proficiency assessment, E.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting just one enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hem him in and hunt him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He breached our perimeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, arm yourselves! Commit our reserves, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible... Our garrison is company-sized! 200 men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten his {\i1}nom de guerre{\i0}, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The One-man Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Physical abilities and mental faculties, both normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Which leaves him as the only irregularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone still here? We're about to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too scared to move, and you grabbed my hand and dragged me away, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I owed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who's never treated me differently from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be our last look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so maudlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's still in the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to make sure no one was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This vessel will now forcibly dock at Module 77!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, the prisoner is still at large!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Further delays in the escape schedule cannot be tolerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto Tokishima, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're— Yamada, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over that robot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get even for Nobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards can run away if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that! It's—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna be the hero and hog all the glory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all running! We're all going to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure this is where I saw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No lifesigns! No thermal signatures detected!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gate has been secured!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Change alert level. All hands, conduct check.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Course is clear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Course is clear, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I worried over nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoke? An enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fall back! Emergency reverse'{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake? I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've run aground?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir. In our current condition, carrying out a large ship would be difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it... We're trapped here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, what they're saying? We can't escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer us, soldier man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:24.02,Alt,,0,0,0,,You're gonna save us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any information?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A riot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, that Dorssian prisoner is behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! A single prisoner couldn't do all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is no ordinary prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't abandon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down! Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A hand mic... An earthquake... A riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true? ARUS is your source?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I heard it from a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A student? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,3:14PM... The answer lies behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Him! He said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Plan D7 complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You? You're the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a pact with me, Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to liberate Dorssia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.56,0:24:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 4, The Hostage is Valvrave".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave... The system that will expose the truth of the world.
